{
  "id": "nce2-l66",
  "title": "Lesson 66: Sweet as Honey",
  "audio": "/audio/nce2/66－Sweet as Honey.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What was 'sweet as honey' and why?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.69,
      "endTime": 16.03,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "In 1963 a Lancaster bomber crashed on Wallis Island,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 16.04,
      "endTime": 22.4
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "a remote place in the South Pacific, a long way west of Samoa.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 22.41,
      "endTime": 28.59
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The plane wasn't too badly damaged,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.6,
      "endTime": 31.6,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Too",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "也"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but over the years the crash was forgotten and the wreck remained undisturbed.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 31.61,
      "endTime": 38.57
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Then in 1989, twenty-six years after the crash, the plane was accidentally rediscovered in an aerial survey of the island.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 38.58,
      "endTime": 51.33
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "By this time, a Lancaster bomber in reasonable condition was rare and worth rescuing.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.34,
      "endTime": 59.88,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The French authorities had the plane packaged and moved in parts back to France.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 59.89,
      "endTime": 66.27,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "French",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "法国的，法语"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Now a group of enthusiasts are going to have the plane restored.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.28,
      "endTime": 71.63,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It has four Rolls-Royce Merlin engines but the group will need to have only three of them rebuilt.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 71.64,
      "endTime": 80.43,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Imagine their surprise and delight when they broke open the packing cases",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.44,
      "endTime": 86.62,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and found that the fourth engine was sweet as honey--still in perfect condition.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 86.63,
      "endTime": 94.2,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "A colony of bees had turned the engine into a hive and it was totally preserved in beeswax!",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 94.21,
      "endTime": 99.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
